</div>
                        
                        <p>Born with a partial clubfoot, she may not have shown signs at a young age&nbsp;of&nbsp;the graceful athlete she would become in Chapel Hill and beyond. But regardless of the shade of blue on her collegiate uniform, Hamm remains a role model for girls both young and old. </p>
<p>As Scott would have said, she’s “as cool as the other side of the pillow.”</p>

